<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <title></title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Welcome to the Mystery Word game.</h1><br>
    <p>The computer will select a word at random for you to guess.</p><br>
    <p>You may then guess a letter to see if it appears in the word. If it does, those letters will be revealed.</p><br>
    <p>If it does not, you will lose one guess.</p><br>
    <p>You win if you can guess all the letters with less than 8 incorrect guesses.</p><br>
    <form action="/launch" method="post">
      <button type="submit" value="Submit" id="startButton">Click to Play!</button>
    </form>
  </body>
</html>
